Sentencas: A hydrogen and oxygen electrochemical pump technique has been employed to elucidate the conduction of proton and oxygen ion in a doped ceria-carbonate composite electrolyte for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Validation of H+/O2- conduction in doped ceria-carbonate composite material using an electrochemical pumping method

Sentencas: The composite material shows efficient conductivities of both of the two ions at 650 degrees C.
Titulo: Validation of H+/O2- conduction in doped ceria-carbonate composite material using an electrochemical pumping method

Sentencas: The molten carbonate phase is important for the migration of both of the two ions.
Titulo: Validation of H+/O2- conduction in doped ceria-carbonate composite material using an electrochemical pumping method

Sentencas: The mechanism of the conduction of proton and oxygen ion is also discussed.
Titulo: Validation of H+/O2- conduction in doped ceria-carbonate composite material using an electrochemical pumping method
